rows.label: tlk00040105_msg0001
rows.name:
There's no telling what you'll find
in an undiscovered region.
Best to remain vigilant.

rows.label: tlk00040105_msg0003
rows.name:
Still, you'll be with a bunch of Drivers.
Drivers have incredible strength, so
you'll probably be fine with them.

rows.label: tlk00040105_msg0004
rows.name:
You just concentrate on fulfilling
your role in the mission!
